## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f94af-227">취소할 수 있는 이벤트입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f94af-227">This is a cancelable event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f94af-228">설정의 <xref:Microsoft.Win32.SessionEndingEventArgs.Cancel%2A> 속성을 `true` 는 세션이 계속 실행 되도록 요청 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f94af-228">Setting the <xref:Microsoft.Win32.SessionEndingEventArgs.Cancel%2A> property to `true` will request that the session continues to run.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f94af-229">세션이 종료 될 했더라도 제공 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f94af-229">It provides no guarantee that the session will not end.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f94af-230">사용 중인 경우 <xref:Microsoft.Win32.SystemEvents.SessionEnding> 시스템 로그 오프 하거나 다시 부팅을 검색 하는 Windows form에가 결정할 수 있는 결정적인 방법은 없습니다 여부는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.Closing> 이벤트가이 이벤트 전에 발생 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f94af-230">If you are using <xref:Microsoft.Win32.SystemEvents.SessionEnding> in a Windows form to detect a system logoff or reboot, there is no deterministic way to decide whether the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.Closing> event will fire before this event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f94af-231">전에 특정 작업을 수행 하려면 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.Closing> 은 했는지 확인 해야 할 발생 <xref:Microsoft.Win32.SystemEvents.SessionEnding> 보다 먼저 실행 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.Closing>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f94af-231">If you want to perform some special tasks before <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.Closing> is fired, you need to ensure that <xref:Microsoft.Win32.SystemEvents.SessionEnding> fires before <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.Closing>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f94af-232">이 작업을 수행 하려면를 트래핑 하는 `WM_QUERYENDSESSION` 재정의 하 여 폼에는 `WndProc` 함수입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f94af-232">To do this, you need to trap the `WM_QUERYENDSESSION` in the form by overriding the `WndProc` function.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="f94af-233">이 예제에서는이 작업을 수행 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f94af-233">This example demonstrates how to do this.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Private Shared WM_QUERYENDSESSION As Integer = &H11  
 Private Shared systemShutdown As Boolean = False  
 Protected Overrides Sub WndProc(ByRef m As System.Windows.Forms.Message)  
     If m.Msg = WM_QUERYENDSESSION Then  
         MessageBox.Show("queryendsession: this is a logoff, shutdown, or reboot")  
         systemShutdown = True  
     End If  
     ' If this is WM_QUERYENDSESSION, the closing event should be raised in the base WndProc.  
     MyBase.WndProc(m)  
 End Sub 'WndProc   
 Private Sub Form1_Closing(ByVal sender As System.Object, ByVal e As System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs) Handles MyBase.Closing  
     If (systemShutdown) Then  
     ' Reset the variable because the user might cancel the shutdown.  
         systemShutdown = False  
         If (System.Windows.Forms.DialogResult.Yes = _  
                 MessageBox.Show("My application", "Do you want to save your work before logging off?", MessageBoxButtons.YesNo)) Then  
                 e.Cancel = True  
         Else  
                 e.Cancel = False  
         End If  
     End If  
 End Sub  
  
```  
  
```csharp  
private static int WM_QUERYENDSESSION = 0x11;  
private static bool systemShutdown = false;  
protected override void WndProc(ref System.Windows.Forms.Message m)  
{  
    if (m.Msg==WM_QUERYENDSESSION)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("queryendsession: this is a logoff, shutdown, or reboot");  
        systemShutdown = true;  
    }  
  
    // If this is WM_QUERYENDSESSION, the closing event should be  
    // raised in the base WndProc.  
    base.WndProc(ref m);  
  
} //WndProc   
  
private void Form1_Closing(  
    System.Object sender,   
    System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs e)  
{  
    if (systemShutdown)  
        // Reset the variable because the user might cancel the   
        // shutdown.  
    {  
        systemShutdown = false;  
        if (DialogResult.Yes==MessageBox.Show("My application",   
            "Do you want to save your work before logging off?",   
            MessageBoxButtons.YesNo))  
        {  
            e.Cancel = true;  
        }  
        else  
        {  
            e.Cancel = false;  
        }  
    }  
}  
```  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="f94af-234">콘솔 응용 프로그램을 일으키지 않습니다는 <xref:Microsoft.Win32.SystemEvents.SessionEnding> 이벤트입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f94af-234">Console applications do not raise the <xref:Microsoft.Win32.SystemEvents.SessionEnding> event.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="f94af-235">이 이벤트는 메시지 펌프 실행 하는 경우에 발생 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f94af-235">This event is only raised if the message pump is running.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f94af-236">Windows 서비스의 숨겨진된 폼이 사용 되거나 메시지 펌프를 수동으로 시작 하지 않는 한이 이벤트 되지 발생 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f94af-236">In a Windows service, unless a hidden form is used or the message pump has been started manually, this event will not be raised.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f94af-237">Windows 서비스의 숨겨진된 폼을 사용 하 여 시스템 이벤트를 처리 하는 방법을 보여 주는 코드 예제를 참조 하십시오.는 <xref:Microsoft.Win32.SystemEvents> 클래스입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f94af-237">For a code example that shows how to handle system events by using a hidden form in a Windows service, see the <xref:Microsoft.Win32.SystemEvents> class.</span></span>  
  
> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="f94af-238">정적 이벤트 이기 때문에 메모리 누수가 발생 하거나 응용 프로그램이 삭제 될 때 이벤트 처리기를 분리 해야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f94af-238">Because this is a static event, you must detach your event handlers when your application is disposed, or memory leaks will result.</span></span>
